<plot>Dance instructors Herman and Pat visit Hugo Sinclair, a devout believer in spiritualism. Pat wants to speak with Sinclair about his daughter Ruth, but SInclair is intent on an upcoming seance conducted by two distinguished guests. Pat and Herman, hiding, are terrorized during the seance, but once they discover the guests are frauds, they do a little terrorizing themselves.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?537693</url></doc>
